description.en:
What is the project about?
A MEME token

What makes your project unique?
An interesting meme token, we are making the community hot, at the same time, we are working hard to develop the substantive application of the token

History of your project.

This is our first project, this is a starting point, we have many experienced members
What’s next for your project?
At present, we have launched MEXC, our next goal is to launch more CEX, and we are currently discussing with more listing leaders

What can your token be used for?
This is an interesting memecoin. We will start our substantive application after more people know us. We are currently developing the application path, which will not be long
